---
// HowItWorks.astro — "Cómo hacer un pedido"
// 3 pasos simples, diseño moderno con línea conectora
---

<section id="como-funciona" class="hiw">
  <div class="hiw-inner">

    <div class="hiw-header reveal">
      <div class="hiw-tag">Simple y rápido</div>
      <h2>¿Cómo hago<br/><em>mi pedido?</em></h2>
      <p class="hiw-sub">En tres pasos, tu torta lista para el evento</p>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw-steps">

      <!-- Paso 1 -->
      <div class="hiw-step reveal">
        <div class="hiw-step-num">01</div>
        <div class="hiw-step-icon">🎂</div>
        <h3>Elegís tu torta</h3>
        <p>Usá el configurador para elegir el tamaño y los rellenos que más te gusten. ¡Hay 12 opciones!</p>
        <a href="#pedidos" class="hiw-step-cta">Configurar ahora →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Conector -->
      <div class="hiw-connector" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hiw-connector-line"></div>
        <div class="hiw-connector-arrow">›</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 2 -->
      <div class="hiw-step reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="hiw-step-num">02</div>
        <div class="hiw-step-icon">💬</div>
        <h3>Me escribís</h3>
        <p>El pedido me llega directamente a WhatsApp. Te confirmo disponibilidad y precio al instante.</p>
        <p class="hiw-step-note">⏱ Con 5 días de anticipación</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Conector -->
      <div class="hiw-connector" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hiw-connector-line"></div>
        <div class="hiw-connector-arrow">›</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 3 -->
      <div class="hiw-step reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="hiw-step-num">03</div>
        <div class="hiw-step-icon">🎉</div>
        <h3>Retirás en Salto</h3>
        <p>Pasás a buscar tu torta por el domicilio en Salto, Buenos Aires. Lista para sorprender.</p>
        <p class="hiw-step-note">📍 Salto, Buenos Aires</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- CTA final -->
    <div class="hiw-cta reveal">
      <a href="#pedidos" class="hiw-btn-main">
        🎂 Quiero hacer mi pedido
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/5492474453333?text=Hola%20Viviana!%20Tengo%20una%20consulta%20antes%20de%20hacer%20mi%20pedido"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="hiw-btn-secondary"
      >
        💬 Tengo una pregunta
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hiw {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FDFBF7 0%, #F9F3EF 100%);
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Decoración de fondo sutil */
  .hiw::before {
    content: '🎂';
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 12rem;
    opacity: 0.03;
    top: -2rem;
    right: -2rem;
    pointer-events: none;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hiw-inner {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Header */
  .hiw-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .hiw-tag {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rosa-viejo);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .hiw-tag::before, .hiw-tag::after {
    content: '';
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rosa-viejo);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .hiw-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--grafito);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .hiw-header h2 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--rosa-oscuro);
  }

  .hiw-sub {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: #999;
  }

  /* Steps layout */
  .hiw-steps {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  /* Conector entre pasos */
  .hiw-connector {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 3.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
  }

  .hiw-connector-line {
    width: 100%;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--rosa-viejo), var(--dorado-claro));
    opacity: 0.4;
    margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
  }

  .hiw-connector-arrow {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--rosa-viejo);
    opacity: 0.5;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-top: -0.5rem;
  }

  /* Cada paso */
  .hiw-step {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,165,165,0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }

  .hiw-step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 36px rgba(212,165,165,0.2);
  }

  .hiw-step-num {
    position: absolute;
    top: -14px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rosa-viejo), var(--rosa-oscuro));
    color: white;
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .hiw-step-icon {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08));
  }

  .hiw-step h3 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--grafito);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .hiw-step p {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.80rem;
    color: #777;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hiw-step-note {
    font-size: 0.72rem !important;
    color: var(--rosa-viejo) !important;
    font-weight: 600 !important;
    background: var(--rosa-claro);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .hiw-step-cta {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--rosa-oscuro);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    transition: gap 0.2s;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .hiw-step-cta:hover {
    color: var(--grafito);
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* CTA final */
  .hiw-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .hiw-btn-main {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rosa-viejo), var(--rosa-oscuro));
    color: white;
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(184,133,126,0.4);
  }

  .hiw-btn-main:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(184,133,126,0.5);
  }

  .hiw-btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: white;
    color: var(--grafito);
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(212,165,165,0.35);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .hiw-btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--rosa-viejo);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(212,165,165,0.2);
  }

  /* ── MOBILE ── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hiw {
      padding: 4rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .hiw-steps {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hiw-connector {
      /* En mobile el conector es vertical */
      flex-direction: row;
      padding-top: 0;
      padding-left: 3rem;
      width: auto;
      height: 28px;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0;
    }

    .hiw-connector-line {
      width: 2px;
      height: 28px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--rosa-viejo), var(--dorado-claro));
    }

    .hiw-connector-arrow {
      position: absolute;
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      margin: 0;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .hiw-step {
      padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .hiw-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .hiw-btn-main,
    .hiw-btn-secondary {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
